'''螺絲粉'''（'''Fusilli'''，{{IPA-it|fuˈzilli|}}）一種[[螺旋|螺旋]]狀的的[[義大利麵|義大利麵]]，挤压成型。<ref>[https://www.mashed.com/447536/fusilli-vs-rotini-whats-the-difference/| Fusilli Vs Rotini: What's The Difference?]</ref> <ref>[https://www.thespruceeats.com/what-is-fusilli-995688/ What Is Fusilli?]</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=The meaning of pasta names - OxfordWords blog|url=https://blog.oxforddictionaries.com/2014/10/24/butterflies-worms-linguistic-look-pasta-world-pasta-day/|accessdate=25 November 2017|work=OxfordWords blog|date=24 October 2014|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201035012/https://blog.oxforddictionaries.com/2014/10/24/butterflies-worms-linguistic-look-pasta-world-pasta-day/|dead-url=no}}</ref>螺絲粉是最常见的意大利面食之一，其外观和[[螺絲粉_(Gemelli)|螺絲粉 (Gemelli)]]极像。在[[台灣|台灣]]又名螺旋麵，經常做為[[牛排|牛排]]旁邊的配菜之一。

